
● Summary: LifePath as Domain #14 - The Destination

  Architectural Change

  LifePath is now recognized as the 14th domain - The Destination - not just a meta-service. Reports has been demoted to a cross-cutting system (meta-service for read-only aggregation).

  Changes Made

  1. /core/utils/services_bootstrap.py
  # The Destination - LifePath (Domain #14)
  # "Everything flows toward the life path"
  lifepath: Any = None  # ReportLifePathService - Life goal alignment tracking

  2. /core/models/search/search_router.py
  # The Destination - LifePath (Domain #14)
  # "Everything flows toward the life path"
  EntityType.LIFEPATH: "lifepath",
  EntityType.LIFE_PATH: "lifepath",  # Alias → same service
  # Cross-cutting Systems (not domains)
  EntityType.REPORT: "reports",  # Meta-service: statistical aggregation

  3. /CLAUDE.md - Complete rewrite of architecture section

  The 14-Domain Architecture

  | Group                | Domains                                           | Count |
  |----------------------|---------------------------------------------------|-------|
  | Activity             | Tasks, Goals, Habits, Events, Choices, Principles | 6     |
  | Finance              | Finance                                           | 1     |
  | Curriculum           | KU, LS, LP                                        | 3     |
  | Content/Organization | Journals, Assignments, MOC                        | 3     |
  | The Destination      | LifePath                                          | 1     |
  | Total                |                                                   | 14    |

  Cross-Cutting Systems (5)

  | System      | Purpose                                          |
  |-------------|--------------------------------------------------|
  | UserContext | Identity + ~240 fields of state                  |
  | Search      | Unified search across 14 domains                 |
  | Calendar    | Aggregates Tasks, Events, Habits, Goals          |
  | Askesis     | Life context synthesis + recommendations         |
  | Reports     | READ-ONLY statistical aggregation (meta-service) |

  The Flow

  All 13 domains flow toward LifePath:
  - Goals → SERVES_LIFE_PATH
  - Principles → Guide alignment
  - Habits → Daily behaviors supporting life direction
  - KU/LS/LP → Learning that enables life goals
  - Choices → Decisions evaluated against life path
  - Tasks/Events → Tactical execution
  - Finance → Resource allocation aligned with priorities
  - Journals/Assignments/MOC → Reflection, processing, organization

  LifePath answers the ultimate question: "Am I living my life path?"

